work.work-title: My heart is full of Christ

credit.credit-words: Fairer than all the earth-born race, Perfect in comeliness Thou art; Replenished are Thy lips with grace, And full of love Thy tender heart: God ever blest! we bow the knee, And own all fullness dwells in Thee.
My heart is full of Christ
